rows.label: tlk70000033_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Because of big raid, lots of shortages
of things everywhere. Big problem for
lots of folks!

rows.label: tlk70000033_02_msg0002
rows.name:
So Momimi get Pyrithium Trade Guild
send over relief packages for no money.
Momimi just make it happen.

rows.label: tlk70000033_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Strangely generous act for Momimi, you
say? Actually, holding out Samod to
needypon is family tradition of Momimi.

rows.label: tlk70000033_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Now that friend says, it is strange.
Strange, strange tradition of family of
Momimi...

rows.label: tlk70000033_02_msg0005
rows.name:
But perhaps in future Momimi is
needypon, and will get a Samod
from a kindypon.
